          "example": ["\n<div>\n<code>\nnoFill();\nx1 = 85, x2 = 10, x3 = 90, x4 = 15;\ny1 = 20, y2 = 10, y3 = 90, y4 = 80;\nbezier(x1, y1, x2, y2, x3, y3, x4, y4);\nfill(255);\nsteps = 10;\nfor (i = 0; i <= steps; i++) {\n  t = i / steps;\n  x = bezierPoint(x1, x2, x3, x4, t);\n  y = bezierPoint(y1, y2, y3, y4, t);\n  ellipse(x, y, 5, 5);\n}\n</code>\n</div>"],
